headline.print_headline: Blast in Eastern Kenya Wounds 11: Police
headline.main: Blast in Eastern Kenya Wounds 11: Police

lead_paragraph: A suspected grenade blast near a mosque wounded 11 people in the eastern Kenyan town of Garissa on Tuesday, close to the border with Somalia, police and disaster officials said.
